<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<title>We Received Your Enquiry</title>
</head>

<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f2f4f8;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
<tr>
<td align="center">

<!-- Email Card -->

<table width="620" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
style="background:#ffffff;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #e6e8ec;box-shadow:0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05)">

<!-- Header -->

<tr>
<td style="padding:26px 32px;background:#111827;color:#ffffff;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.3px">
{{accountName}}
</td>
</tr>


<!-- Greeting -->

<tr>
<td style="padding:32px 32px 10px 32px;font-size:15px;color:#374151;line-height:24px">

<p style="margin-top:0;font-size:16px">
Hello <strong>{{name}}</strong>,
</p>

<p>
Thank you for contacting <strong>{{accountName}}</strong>.  
We have successfully received your enquiry and our team will review it shortly.
</p>

</td>
</tr>

<!-- Lead Details -->

<tr>
<td style="padding:0 32px 25px 32px">

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
style="background:#f9fafb;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #e5e7eb">

<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="padding:14px 18px;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#111827;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb">
Submitted Details
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="padding:12px 18px;font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;width:140px">Name</td>
<td style="padding:12px 18px;font-size:14px;color:#111827">{{name}}</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="padding:12px 18px;font-size:13px;color:#6b7280">Email</td>
<td style="padding:12px 18px;font-size:14px;color:#111827">{{email}}</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="padding:12px 18px;font-size:13px;color:#6b7280">Phone</td>
<td style="padding:12px 18px;font-size:14px;color:#111827">{{phone}}</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="padding:12px 18px;font-size:13px;color:#6b7280">Source</td>
<td style="padding:12px 18px;font-size:14px;color:#111827">{{source}}</td>
</tr>

</table>

</td>
</tr>

<!-- Message -->

<tr>
<td style="padding:0 32px 25px 32px;font-size:15px;color:#374151;line-height:24px">

<p>
Our team will get back to you soon.  
If you need to add more information, simply reply to this email.
</p>

</td>
</tr>

<!-- Support Section -->

<tr>
<td style="padding:22px 32px;background:#fafafa;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb">

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
<tr>

<td style="font-size:14px;color:#374151">
Need help?
</td>

<td align="right">
<a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}"
style="background:#111827;color:#ffffff; margin-left: 12px; padding:10px 16px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px">
Contact Support
</a>
</td>

</tr>
</table>

<p style="margin-top:10px;font-size:13px;color:#6b7280">
{{supportEmail}}
</p>

</td>
</tr>

<!-- Footer -->

<tr>
<td style="padding:28px 32px;background:#f9fafb;font-size:13px;color:#6b7280">

<p style="margin:0 0 8px 0">
Best Regards,<br>
<strong>{{accountName}} Team</strong>
</p>

<p style="margin:8px 0 0 0">
© {{year}} {{accountName}}. All rights reserved.
</p>

<p style="margin-top:14px;font-size:12px;color:#9ca3af">
You received this email because you submitted an enquiry through
<strong>{{source.name}}</strong>.
</p>

</td>
</tr>

</table>

</td>
</tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>
